title: 15. What We Want For Our Highest Selves in 2020
description: Hi friends, Lauren + Tess here. In this episode we are talking about objectives for 2020-- and what we envision our highest selves doing in our daily lives, from hair care to fitness to client interactions. Please let me know what you think and feel free to DM us if you have any questions or want to discuss this topic further!
